          <h2 id="cleaning-protocol">Cleaning Protocol for Pet Stays</h2>
          <p>A rigorous turnover process is what separates hosts who have great experiences with pet guests from those who don't. The goal is to eliminate all evidence of a pet before the next guests arrive, including guests who may have allergies.</p>

          <h3>Extra Steps for Pet Turnovers</h3>
          <div class="alternatives-grid">
