            </div>
            <div class="alternative-card">
              <span class="alt-number">2</span>
              <h4>Lint Roll Everything Fabric</h4>
              <p>Lint roll all throws, cushions, lamp shades, fabric headboards, and any decorative pillows. This catches fine pet hair that vacuums miss. Keep a large supply of lint rollers in your cleaning kit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

