              <p>Pet odor is the number one complaint from subsequent guests. Open all windows for at least 30 minutes regardless of the season. Use a light, neutral deodorizer (not heavily scented, which can trigger its own complaints) on fabric surfaces.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="alternative-card">
